rows.label: qst300409_msg0001
rows.name:
I don't know where you are
getting your information from...

rows.label: qst300409_msg0002
rows.name:
But your actions here are in
direct opposition to the interests
of Superbia!

rows.label: qst300409_msg0051
rows.name: I know nothing of an heir.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0052
rows.name:
Our lord merely suggested that we use
the rumors from the Succession War
to make our claim sound legitimate.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0053
rows.name:
There's no point asking after our lord.
He will already have escaped to a safe
location by now. You'll never find him!

rows.label: qst300409_msg0071
rows.name:
We have already informed our lord
that you people were snooping around.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0072
rows.name:
I'm sure he will already have escaped
to somewhere you will never find him!

rows.label: qst300409_msg0073
rows.name:
He was the one who came up with
the idea to take advantage of the wild
rumors of an Envian heir, you know.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0101
rows.name:
This is the key to the room where
the Jeweled Signet is hidden.
Do with it as you wish.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0102
rows.name: I am the captain of this vessel.

rows.label: qst300409_msg0103
rows.name:
I value the safety of my ship and its
crew over securing an item for a client
who will already have gone into hiding...

rows.label: qst300409_msg0104
rows.name:
If we resist you any further, I doubt
this ship would stay unharmed for long.
